This product wraps or interacts with the following open-source components,
each governed by its own license:

  * RDKit (BSD-3-Clause)               — cheminformatics primitives
  * GROMACS (LGPL-2.1+)                — molecular dynamics engine
  * AutoDock-GPU (Apache-2.0)          — GPU molecular docking
  * OpenFold (Apache-2.0)              — protein structure prediction
  * Boltz (MIT)                        — protein co-folding
  * Chai-1 (Apache-2.0)                — protein co-folding
  * Gnina (Apache-2.0)                 — CNN-scored docking
  * MDAnalysis / MDTraj (GPL-2.0)      — trajectory analysis
  * PDBFixer (MIT)                     — protein preparation
  * OpenMM (MIT)                       — MD toolkit
  * xTB / CREST (LGPL-3.0)             — quantum-mechanical methods
  * AIMNet2 / MACE / ANI-2x            — neural network potentials
  * Chemprop (MIT)                     — message-passing property models
  * CatBoost (Apache-2.0)              — gradient boosting
  * FastAPI (MIT), httpx (BSD-3)       — HTTP surfaces
  * Model Context Protocol (MIT)      — the MCP specification

These components are NOT redistributed in this repository; they are
declared as runtime dependencies and installed via `pip install -r
requirements.txt` (Python) or their upstream distribution channels.

